gitleaks stdin mode does not load detection rules (confirmed v8.30).
The inline scan in cmd_note works around this by writing to a tmpfile
and scanning with gitleaks dir. This adds ~5ms latency per note write.

If a future gitleaks version fixes stdin, simplify back to pipe mode.
Track: https://github.com/gitleaks/gitleaks/issues
